{"tid":2018963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如搞個眾籌行動","createTime":"2020-05-16T03:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T04:48:51.000Z","uid":134033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b87922b1a2dd6456c73dad27dce68858d7acf169","tid":2018963,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"利申番先  出院冇耐  唔敢做搞手<br />\n<br />\n但眼見手足被判幾年 <br />\n<br />\n接下來只會有更多暴政同痴線既場面<br />\n<br />\n呢種既法治同判刑 作為一個有良知 同理心既人<br />\n<br />\n實在係令人髮指<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多  既然好多行動都要作出犧牲<br />\n<br />\n要占前顧後  人數又未回歸 各種因素<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如就用我地黃圈最多 且最有特色既野<br />\n<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟只係dum個諗法出來 希望有有心人搞大佢<br />\n<br />\n如果有方法 有link 可以捐到錢比<br />\n<br />\n任何 被判監 等緊結果 經濟有困難既手足<br />\n<br />\n就算係網頁 好似貨咁放哂手足 基本安全資料咁去捐<br />\n<br />\n都冇咩所謂  幫到手足就ok<br />\n<br />\n當然最好係fc左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論 最好就係直接行動"},{"pid":"0e026b354259ce3bb40d54aff9684792d3a398c5","tid":2018963,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:16:05.000Z","msg":"推阿屌"},{"pid":"8ae6779f9b189678036978849d3b78f4df5e4ae2","tid":2018963,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a7598e7c5b3c1cba1edbd9f48b30ee49967cc","tid":2018963,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695fc9